               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Liturgical miscellanea (fols. 1v-29r)
 - ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... “I worship Thee…” (fols. 3ra-4v)
 - Ṣalota ʿǝṭan “Prayer
                     of Incense” (fols. 6ra-8ra)
 - Fǝtḥat za-wald “Absolution of the Son”
                     (fols. 13va-15ra)
 II) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary” (fols.
                     30r-42v)
 II-1) Introductory exhortation (fols. 30r-34r)
 II-2) Taʾammǝra
                     Māryām: 5 miracles (fols. 34v-42r)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1"/>
                     <title>Liturgical texts</title>

